    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning, at 6th level your Superiority Die begins to grow in strength as you do.</p><p>Your Superiority Die grows 1 step, into a D6.</p><p>It repeats this process at 9th (d8), 14th (d10) and 17th levels (d12).</p><p>Additionally, once per turn whenever you would score a critical hit with an attack roll or roll a natural 20 on a saving throw you regain 1 Superiority Die.</p><p></p>",
